Coding Style for pyquarkchain Project

=============
General Rules

Follow PEP8 https://www.python.org/dev/peps/pep-0008/
For sublime, we suggest to use Anaconda package.

======
Naming

- Package name: lower_case_with_underscore
- Class name: UpperCamelCase
- Method name: lower_case_with_underscore
- Constant: UPPER_CASE_WITH_UNDERSCORE
- Global function: lower_case_with_underscore
- Local variable: lower_case_with_underscore

==============
Code Formatter

All py files should be formatted using the Black code formatter.
https://github.com/ambv/black
